The Choke devil is a superior variant of the normal dust devil. It has a chance of spawning once after purchasing the unlock Bigger and Badder for 150 Slayer reward points from any Slayer master.

Similar to their lower-level counterparts, a facemask or slayer helmet is required to safely engage them, as otherwise the player will take rapid damage and have their stats drained.

Drops[edit | edit source]

In addition to 100% drops and tertiary drops, superior slayer monsters will always roll 3 additional items, of which only 1 roll may be from the superior unique table. The other rolls are performed on the regular counterpart's table; their displayed drop chances represent a single roll.

Drop rates estimated based on 784,134 kills from the Drop Rate Project, unless otherwise cited.

The average Choke devil kill is worth 81,267.32.

The average Choke devil kill while on a Konar task is worth 83,405.38.
